color:#24292E\">  email: </span><span style=\"color:#032F62\">\"zhangsan@mail.com\"</span><span style=\"color:#24292E\">,</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#24292E\">  createdAt: </span><span style=\"color:#D73A49\">new</span><span style=\"color:#6F42C1\"> Date</span><span style=\"color:#24292E\">()</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#24292E\">};</span></span></code></pre>",
